## ⚡ Performance

Core simulation loop compiled using:

```python
@numba.njit(fastmath=True)
```

| Particles | Speedup   |
| --------- | --------- |
| 500       | ~100–300× |
| 2000      | ~100–300× |

> One-time JIT cost (~1–3s), then cached.

Run benchmark:

```bash
jupyter notebook benchmark.ipynb
```

